Field Detail

playerName

public java.lang.String playerName
The value that will be passed as the 'player' parameter for all analytics events. You can use this to organize analytics data coming from multiple apps or different types of players within an app. The default value is the application label for the app running this component.

destination

public java.lang.String destination
The value that will be passed as the 'destination' parameter for all analytics events. The default value is a marketplace URL.
